column1: DFLEXLIBS_001,,,"For each HVAC zone in the building, what are the timeseries IDs for the available zone temperature sensor' points, min and max temperature setpoints, temperature setpoints (single, heating/cooling or occupied/unoccupied), occupancy sensors and commands, and any related VAV damper, discharge temperature, and reheat command points?",lbl/cborg-coder,"ModelRequest(parts=[UserPromptPart(content=""Question: For each HVAC zone in the building, what are the timeseries IDs for the available zone temperature sensor' points, min and max temperature setpoints, temperature setpoints (single, heating/cooling or occupied/unoccupied), occupancy sensors and commands, and any related VAV damper, discharge temperature, and reheat command points?"", timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 24, 17, 52, 14, 407797, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), part_kind='user-prompt')], instructions=None, kind='request')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.2/Brick#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>\\n\\nSELECT ?zone ?zoneLabel\\n       ?tempSensorId ?minSetpointId ?maxSetpointId\\n       ?heatSetpointId ?coolSetpointId ?occupiedSetpointId ?unoccupiedSetpointId\\n       ?occupancySensorId ?occupancyCommandId\\n       ?vav ?damperId ?dischargeTempId ?reheatCmdId\\nWHERE {\\n  # ---- HVAC zones -------------------------------------------------------\\n  ?zone a brick:HVAC_Zone .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel . }\\n\\n  # ---- Zone temperature sensor ------------------------------------------\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?tempSensor .\\n    ?tempSensor a brick:Temperature_Sensor .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?tempSensor brick:hasTimeseriesId ?tempSensorId . }\\n  }\\n\\n  # ---- Min / Max temperature setpoints ---------------------------------\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?minSet .\\n    ?minSet a brick:Min_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?minSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?minSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?maxSet .\\n    ?maxSet a brick:Max_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?maxSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?maxSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n\\n  # ---- Temperature setpoints (heating / cooling / occupied / unoccupied) -----\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?heatSet .\\n    ?heatSet a brick:Heating_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?heatSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?heatSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?coolSet .\\n    ?coolSet a brick:Cooling_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?coolSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?coolSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?occupiedSet .\\n    ?occupiedSet a brick:Occupied_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?occupiedSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?occupiedSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?unoccupiedSet .\\n    ?unoccupiedSet a brick:Unoccupied_Temperature_Setpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?unoccupiedSet brick:hasTimeseriesId ?unoccupiedSetpointId . }\\n  }\\n\\n  # ---- Occupancy sensor and command -------------------------------------\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?occSensor .\\n    ?occSensor a brick:Occupancy_Sensor .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?occSensor brick:hasTimeseriesId ?occupancySensorId . }\\n  }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone brick:hasPoint ?occCommand .\\n    ?occCommand a brick:Occupancy_Command .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?occCommand brick:hasTimeseriesId ?occupancyCommandId . }\\n  }\\n\\n  # ---- VAV serving the zone and its associated points -------------------\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?vav a brick:VAV .\\n    ?vav brick:feeds ?zone .\\n    # VAV damper\\n    OPTIONAL {\\n      ?vav brick:hasPoint ?damper .\\n      ?damper a brick:Damper .\\n      OPTIONAL { ?damper brick:hasTimeseriesId ?damperId . }\\n    }\\n    # Discharge air temperature sensor\\n    OPTIONAL {\\n      ?vav brick:hasPoint ?disTemp .\\n      ?disTemp a brick:Discharge_Air_Temperature_Sensor .\\n      OPTIONAL { ?disTemp brick:hasTimeseriesId ?dischargeTempId . }\\n    }\\n    # Reheat command\\n    OPTIONAL {\\n      ?vav brick:hasPoint ?reheatCmd .\\n      ?reheatCmd a brick:Reheat_Command .\\n      OPTIONAL { ?reheatCmd brick:hasTimeseriesId ?reheatCmdId . }\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 24, 17, 52, 14, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
